Headline: NASA's James Webb Telescope Discovers Evidence of Ancient Galaxies

Article: NASA's James Webb Space Telescope has identified evidence of ancient galaxies forming just a few hundred million years after the Big Bang. The discovery is expected to shed light on the early stages of the universe and the evolution of stars and galaxies.
label: Real

Headline: Alien Spaceship Found Under the Atlantic Ocean, Scientists Confirm

Article: Scientists from an undisclosed organization have confirmed the discovery of a fully intact alien spaceship buried under the Atlantic Ocean. The spaceship is said to be 100,000 years old and contains advanced technologies.
label: Fake
